          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If you don’t implement this method, then the results table is reloaded as soon as the scope button selection changes."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You might implement this method if you want to perform an asynchronous search: you would initiate the search in this method, then return "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/no"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", and reload the table when you have results."
            }
          ]
        }
